##  join my patreon!

i make monthly goodies over on Patreon for my regular supporters! You can
pledge an amount ranging from $1 - $15, which you can edit and cancel any
time.

Rewards include things like digital downloads, exclusive videos, sketchbook
tours, early access to shop updates, and monthly prints and stickers delivered
to your door. You also get an exclusive discount to the shop and access to the
secret shop!

Become a Patron!
